node.title: Police seek sightings of woman after her clothes were found on beach
node.content: ["Taup\u014d police have concerns for the well-being of a woman whose clothes were found on Kinloch Beach.", "Jan-Marie Burton was reported missing by her family on Wednesday.", "She was last seen at around 4pm and items of her clothing have been located on Kinloch Beach, near the boat ramp on Kinloch Esplanade, police say.", "\"Police and her family are concerned for her wellbeing.\"", "Anyone who may have seen her after 4pm Wednesday or has information about her whereabouts is urged to call 111 and quote event number P049123823."]
